 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EBerlin Promotion Agency GmbH \u0026amp; Co.KG (BPA) is a German provider of direct marketing services, sales promotion services and event support services. Founded in early 2007 as a non-commercial project by a group of students from the University of Applied Sciences and the Freie Universit\u00e4t (Free University). The company now employs 4,500 freelancers working in the fields of marketing, mystery check and event support in Germany and runs branch offices in Berlin and Hamburg.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EBPA manages campaigns for international clients in Germany and to date the company has worked with clients from more than 13 countries in Europe, the Middle East, the US and Central Asia. It is also a major supplier of Event Marketing Solutions. The portfolio of the company includes projects for 20th Century Fox, BlackBerry, Fitness First, Lenovo,the UEFA, ADIDAS and Telef\u00f3nica Germany.\u003C/p\u003E",
